==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Izedi
<hw>Iz"e*di</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of an Oriental
religious sect which worships Satan or the Devil.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>Izedis</qex> or Yezdis, the so-called Devil worshipers,
still remain a numerous though oppressed people in Mesopotamia and
adjacent countries.</q> <rj><qau>Tylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Izedism</ent>⟦br⟧
